The paper discusses the task of computational advertising, which involves selecting the most suitable advertisement candidate from a set of possible options. This task involves machine learning algorithms and causal inference techniques. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science).
